      "title": "Disappointed!",
      "body": "After researching several filters and trying a few less expensive filters, I had high hopes for Filterbaby. Unfortunately, my hopes were dashed. The water pressure in my shower has dropped significantly after only 10 days of use. This product is a “no go” and will have to be removed. Buyer beware!",
